---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Berrystock Solutions">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/src/styles/home-modern.css" />

  <div class="home-wrap">
    <section class="home-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="kicker">Berrystock Solutions</div>
        <h1 class="h-title">We deliver cloud, ERP, and AI systems that actually get adopted.</h1>
        <p class="h-lead">
          Secure cloud platforms. ERP and CRM integration. Real estate automation. AI workflows with controls.
          Built end-to-end, deployed cleanly, and handed over with a runbook.
        </p>

        <div class="actions">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/contact">Get in touch</a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/work">See proof</a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/services">Solutions</a>
        </div>

        <div class="badges">
          <span class="badge">Senior-only delivery</span>
          <span class="badge">Security-first</span>
          <span class="badge">System integration</span>
          <span class="badge">Automation-led</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="home-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="grid-2">
          <div class="panel">
            <p class="problem">You bought the tools. The pilots never scaled. Nothing stuck.</p>
            <p class="p">
              Most teams don’t fail because they lack software. They fail because there’s no platform foundation,
              no operating model, and no integration plan. We fix that.
            </p>
            <ul class="list">
              <li>Cloud foundations that support security and scale</li>
              <li>ERP/CRM integration that matches real workflows</li>
              <li>Automation that has boundaries, auditability, and ownership</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="panel">
            <p class="p"><strong>What we build</strong></p>
            <ul class="list">
              <li><strong>Cloud:</strong> Azure platforms, governance, identity, networking</li>
              <li><strong>ERP/CRM:</strong> deployments, integration, reporting</li>
              <li><strong>AI:</strong> safe automation, agents with controls, event-driven pipelines</li>
              <li><strong>Real estate:</strong> enquiry → qualify → book → sync → report</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="home-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="h2">Trusted by teams that need outcomes</h2>

        <div class="marquee" aria-label="Client logos marquee">
          <div class="track">
            <span class="logo">Property Ops</span>
            <span class="logo">Construction</span>
            <span class="logo">Professional Services</span>
            <span class="logo">Operations Teams</span>
            <span class="logo">SMB to Mid-Market</span>
            <span class="logo">Asset Businesses</span>

            <span class="logo">Property Ops</span>
            <span class="logo">Construction</span>
            <span class="logo">Professional Services</span>
            <span class="logo">Operations Teams</span>
            <span class="logo">SMB to Mid-Market</span>
            <span class="logo">Asset Businesses</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="home-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="h2">How we deliver</h2>

        <div class="steps">
          <div class="step">
            <div class="n">01 • Define</div>
            <h3>Opportunity and architecture</h3>
            <p>
              We identify what’s worth building, design the target state, and define a delivery plan your team can own.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="step">
            <div class="n">02 • Build</div>
            <h3>Platforms, integrations, automation</h3>
            <p>
              Cloud foundations, ERP/CRM integration, and AI automation built with security controls and clear milestones.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="step">
            <div class="n">03 • Adopt</div>
            <h3>Make it stick</h3>
            <p>
              Training, handover, documentation, and operational readiness — so it’s not “a project”, it’s how work gets done.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="home-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="panel cta-box">
          <div>
            <h3>Tell us where you’re at. We’ll map the next move.</h3>
            <p class="p" style="margin-top:8px;">
              A short call to align on outcomes, constraints, and the fastest path to delivery.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="actions" style="margin:0;">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/contact">Get in touch</a>
            <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="mailto:enquiries@berrystocksolutions.co.uk">Email</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>